for all node..left is smaler and right is gretaer.
used for easy searching

recursion jo hai vo directly ans ki taraf bhagti hai.
bda hai to right small hai to left nhi to usi k equal.

isme complexity logn hoti hai..kyu?

phle search mein yah to left jaega yah fir right-> n/2 rah gye.
dusre mein n/4.
isiliye log n

bst v/s bt
jo vbhi chiz structure par depend krti hai jese size,sum to unme dono o(n) mein rhengye.
lekinn jo value par depend krti hai unme logn in bst and o(n) in bt. Example max,min,find.

Diameter vala qustion structure se vasta rkhta hai isilye logn.